&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WE ARE GAME MAKERS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who we are:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are a diverse team of developers driven by a passion for our art, united by our core values and inspired by a culture of inclusivity to build amazing games that thrill players everywhere. We pursue growth and innovation in an environment of safety and trust. Our culture is built on the belief that the more varied voices in our collective will strengthen our team and our games.&amp;nbsp; We are looking for our next teammate who will raise our bar and make us better.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What we need:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are seeking an organized, highly motivated Associate Producer ready to assume responsibility and drive tasks and features forward. In this role, you will develop your production skills by taking ownership of one or more game areas, partnering with the team to plan, update, and execute regular deliveries, alongside limited ownership of full features, departments or a mix of both. You are a collaborative team player who works well with people, processes, and problems to deliver projects on time and at a high standard of quality.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Responsibilities:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul data-path-to-node=&quot;10&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;10,0,0&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-path-to-node=&quot;10,0,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Feature Ownership:&lt;/strong&gt; Act as the Production Feature Owner or Department Feature Owner, partnering to deliver quality and timeliness while managing risk identification and mitigation from concept to completion.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;10,1,0&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-path-to-node=&quot;10,1,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Schedule &amp;amp; Task Management:&lt;/strong&gt; Collaborate with partners to establish long-term schedules, milestone definitions, and sprint goals. Handle daily management, execution, and adjustments of tasks, sprint planning, and structure updates.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;10,2,0&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-path-to-node=&quot;10,2,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Team Coordination &amp;amp; Alignment:&lt;/strong&gt; Actively coordinate with the broader production team to eliminate unnecessary overlap, prevent developer bombardment, and ensure effort isn&#39;t duplicated.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;10,3,0&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-path-to-node=&quot;10,3,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Meeting Facilitation:&lt;/strong&gt; Schedule, attend, and effectively chair meetings. Take clear, concise, and comprehensive notes, outlining actionable next steps, and follow up on resulting action items to completion.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;10,4,0&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-path-to-node=&quot;10,4,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Communication &amp;amp; Updates:&lt;/strong&gt; Supply regular status updates with the right frequency, detail, and clarity via in-person meetings, Slack, email, and Confluence. Effectively communicate milestones and task deadlines to team members.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;10,5,0&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-path-to-node=&quot;10,5,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Quality Assurance &amp;amp; Review:&lt;/strong&gt; Actively coordinate with the team to ensure features are reviewed in-game to driver for quality. Coordinate with QA partners to set testing expectations, managing test plans, specific requests, triage issues, and guarantee show-stopping bugs are dealt with efficiently.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;10,6,0&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-path-to-node=&quot;10,6,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&g

